Welcome to my Ubiquity Plugin for the vb.ly url shortening service. It is very easy to use, you simply foolow these simple steps. 
1. highlight the link that you want to shorten. 
2. Then call your ubiquity window. (using cntrl+spacebar on windows)
3. Type in "vbly" or "vb.ly"
4. look at the preview window and make sure that it is the url that you want to shorten
5. Hit  enter and you will see your highlighted text turn to a shortened link

We will be adding more features to this command so keep on the lookout. If you would like to just subscribe to the plugin without the source code
go to vbshort.hiphopmusiq.com and hit subscribe. Yes, its that simple. 
